text: Héctor A. Díaz (born August 15, 1960) is an American politician. Díaz was born in Manhattan, in New York City, New York. He went to Inter-American University and to Housatonic Community College. Díaz was a caseworker. He lived in Bridgeport, Connecticut. Díaz served in the Connecticut House of Representatives from 1995 to 2001 and was a Democrat.Votesmart.org.-Hector Diaz Connecticut State Library-Connecticut General Assembly Members database ==Notes== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Bridgeport, Connecticut Category:Politicians from Manhattan Category:Connecticut Democrats Category:Members of the Connecticut House of Representatives
